    "body": "Hi @gsiros this doesn't appear to be an issue with HDWalletProvider, but rather with the parameters being passed to `web3.eth.ens.setRecord` -- you may want to change the `ttl` param to something else to get this working. I am sure you have already seen this but here are the [docs](https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.3.4/web3-eth-ens.html#setrecord) for the `setRecord `function.\r\n\r\nI'm closing this issue since it is not a bug with Truffle's code but please feel free to open a new issue if you find that there is something that needs to be investigated on the Truffle side. Thanks!",
